tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  39,33,"And he who brings the Truth and he who confirms (and supports) it - such are the men who do right."
  39,35,"So that Allah will turn off from them (even) the worst in their deeds and give them their reward according to the best of what they have done."
  39,39,"Say: \"O my People! Do whatever ye can: I will do (my part): but soon will ye know-"